OL,3,CChief Constable commissions
OL,4,Cindependent review into Marian
OL,5,CBeattie's murder
OL,7,FUTV understands that Chief Constable
OL,8,FJon Boutcher has commissioned an
OL,9,Findependent review into Marian
OL,10,FBeattie's death, which Bedfordshire
OL,11,FPolice will carry out.
OL,13,FThe 18-year-old was found dead at the
OL,14,Fbottom of a quarry near Aughnacloy, Co
OL,15,FTyrone after attending a dance at
OL,16,FHadden's Garage on the March 30, 1973.
OL,18,FThe Portadown teenager's killer has
OL,19,Fnever been caught.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
