OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772012408
OL,3,CChief Constable commissions
OL,4,Cindependent review into Marian
OL,5,CBeattie's murder
OL,7,FIn June 2025, a Police Ombudsman's
OL,8,Freport exposed numerous failings in
OL,9,Fthe police investigation.
OL,11,FFor over 50 years, her family has
OL,12,Fcontinued to fight for answers.
OL,14,FNot just about who killed Marian, but
OL,15,Falso how the original investigation
OL,16,Fwas handled.
OL,18,FA review is expected to commence in
OL,19,Fthe coming weeks.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
