OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772012408
OL,3,CChief Constable commissions
OL,4,Cindependent review into Marian
OL,5,CBeattie's murder
OL,7,FThe PSNI's Legacy Investigation Branch
OL,8,Fhas said they will contact the family
OL,9,Fto discuss next steps.
OL,11,FIt comes after Marian Beattie's family
OL,12,Fbrought their case directly to
OL,13,FStormont where they met with First
OL,14,FMinister Michelle O'Neill on Tuesday.
OL,16,FMarian's cousin Colette Toman vowed
OL,17,Fthe family's pursuit of justice will
OL,18,Fcontinue.
OL,20,F"Whatever we can do, we'll do and
OL,21,Fwe're determined to do it", she said.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/4
